OL,3,CMother calls for safety improvements
OL,4,Cafter son hit by train at crossing
OL,6,FThe mother of a teenage boy who died
OL,7,Fon a pedestrian level crossing says
OL,8,Fshe never wants another family to go
OL,9,Fthrough the pain they have.
OL,11,F17 year old Harry Basham was hit by a
OL,12,Ftrain on his walk to work in October
OL,13,Fat a foot crossing near Taunton
OL,14,FStation.
OL,16,FThree and a half thousand people have
OL,17,Fsigned a petition calling for urgent
OL,18,Fsafety improvements to the crossing.
