OL,3,CMother calls for safety improvements
OL,4,Cafter son hit by train at crossing
OL,6,FFamily friend Vicky Butland said the
OL,7,Fcrossing is considered high risk, but
OL,8,Fthe current safety features don't
OL,9,Freflect this.
OL,11,FShe said "Once you're on the crossing
OL,12,Fyou don't know a train is coming until
OL,13,Fit is approaching."
OL,15,F"They do sound their horns, but they
OL,16,Fdon't sound their horns out of the
OL,17,Fhours of 7am and 11pm, and Harry was
OL,18,Ftragically killed at 6:55 that
OL,19,Fmorning."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
