OL,3,CMother calls for safety improvements
OL,4,Cafter son hit by train at crossing
OL,6,FThe family and many others want new
OL,7,Fsafety features to be installed at the
OL,8,Fcrossing to try to prevent another
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FVicky said there should be "a traffic
OL,12,Flight system, locking gates, flashing
OL,13,Flights, anything that can alert
OL,14,Fpedestrians to oncoming trains."
OL,16,FThe local MP is backing the campaign
OL,17,Fis meeting Network Rail to discuss the
OL,18,Ffuture of the crossing.
