OL,3,CMother calls for safety improvements
OL,4,Cafter son hit by train at crossing
OL,6,FNetwork Rail said "Our thoughts are
OL,7,Fwith Harry's family and friends and
OL,8,Fthe local community following the
OL,9,Ftragic accident in Taunton in October.
OL,11,F"Network Rail will of course co-
OL,12,Foperate with the inquest and relevant
OL,13,Finvestigations as is appropriate."
OL,15,FHarry's mother Leanne said she just
OL,16,Fdoesn't want it to happen to anyone
OL,17,Felse.
OL,19,F"It's really hard. We didn't get to
OL,20,Fsay goodbye, it was just so sudden and
OL,21,Funexpected."
